	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />How could a light not work with a photosensor? Even if it is too dim (lower contrast ratios are there indeed), just put the Zapper closer to the screen.<br /><br />All the complex stuff in modern light guns is there only to provide a good precision, which is not needed in this case at all.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


